CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper December 27, 1958, pg. 2, reads: "Deceiving - From the outside, this 311 Lowell St. property seems to be in good condition. Inside, however, there are Health Department regulation violations which led to formal charges against Alfred E. Davis. - Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Two and one half story brick house with stained glass windows on second story, 311 Lowell Street, Larimer
